-- Daimler Says It Isn't In Talks With Fiat on Bid to Buy Its Industrial Unit
-- B y   C h r i s   R e i t e r
-- 2010-09-22T08:34:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-22/daimler-denies-repubblica-report-of-talks-with-fiat-on-industrial-unit-bid.html
Daimler AG  said it isn’t in talks
with Fiat SpA about bidding for the Italian carmaker’s
industrial division.  “There are no talks on this with Fiat,” Daimler spokesman
Florian Martens said in a telephone interview today, responding
to a la Repubblica report. “In our industry at this time,
everyone is talking with everyone and so are we.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
